A BIG DOG WITH A BIG PERSONALITY
BROTHERS AND SISTERS I BID YOU BEWARE
OF GIVING YOUR HEART TO A DOG TO TEAR
Kipling  "The Power of the Dog""Ę
┤Please sit and rest and think of
Neal C Thorne
who loved to spend time walking
his past and present dogs.
He will be sadly missed by his wife Elaine and
dog Molly and all his family and friends.
May he be taking a long walk with our
late dog Charlie in the big park in the sky.
14.8,1963 to 16.3.2018"Ž
